---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: tpch[parameterized]_q12"
---
+---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type           | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan        | Sort: lineitem.l_shipmode ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|                     |   Projection: lineitem.l_shipmode, sum(CASE WHEN orders.o_orderpriority = $1 OR orders.o_orderpriority = $2 THEN Int64(1) ELSE Int64(0) END) AS high_line_count, sum(CASE WHEN orders.o_orderpriority != $3 AND orders.o_orderpriority != $4 THEN Int64(1) ELSE Int64(0) END) AS low_line_count                                      |
|                     |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[lineitem.l_shipmode]], aggr=[[sum(CASE WHEN orders.o_orderpriority = $1 OR orders.o_orderpriority = $2 THEN Int64(1) ELSE Int64(0) END), sum(CASE WHEN orders.o_orderpriority != $3 AND orders.o_orderpriority != $4 THEN Int64(1) ELSE Int64(0) END)]]                                                     |
|                     |       Projection: lineitem.l_shipmode, orders.o_orderpriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|                     |         Inner Join: lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|                     |           BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|                     |             TableScan: lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_shipmode], full_filters=[lineitem.l_shipmode = $5 OR lineitem.l_shipmode = $6, lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_commitdate, lineitem.l_receiptdate >= Date32("1994-01-01"), lineitem.l_receiptdate < Date32("1995-01-01")] |
|                     |           BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|                     |             TableScan: orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_orderpriority]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| physical_plan_error | Execution error: Placeholder 'X' was not provided a value for execution.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
